    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When playing media delivered over HTTP, this property is used to determine if the player should automatically delay playback in order to minimize stalling. When this property is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and the player changes from a paused state ("
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1388846-rate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " of "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "0.0"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ") to a played state ("
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1388846-rate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " > "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "0.0"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "), the player will try to determine if the current item can play to its end at the currently specified rate. If it determines that it’s likely to encounter a stall, the value of the player’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1643485-timecontrolstatus"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " will change to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayertimecontrolstatus/avplayertimecontrolstatuswaitingtoplayatspecifiedrate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and playback will automatically start when the likelihood of stalling has been minimized. A similar condition will occur during playback if the current player item’s playback buffer is exhausted and playback stalls. Playback will automatically resume when the likelihood of stalling has been minimized."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You will need to set this property to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " when you require precise control over playback start times, such as if you're are synchronizing multiple player instances using the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1386591-setrate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method. If the value of this property is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", playback will start immediately when requested as long as the playback buffer is not empty. If the playback buffer becomes empty and playback stalls, the player’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1643485-timecontrolstatus"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " will switch to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayertimecontrolstatus/avplayertimecontrolstatuspaused"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and the playback rate will change to "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "0.0"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Changing the value of this property to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " while the player’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1643485-timecontrolstatus"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayertimecontrolstatus/avplayertimecontrolstatuswaitingtoplayatspecifiedrate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1643486-reasonforwaitingtoplay"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayerwaitingtominimizestallsreason"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " will cause the player to immediately attempt playback at the specified rate."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "For clients linked against iOS 10.0 and later or macOS 10.12 and later (and running on those versions), the default value of this property is "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": false,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ". This property did not exist in previous OS versions and the observed behavior was dependent on the type of media played:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "unorderedList",
              "items": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "type": "strong",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "HTTP Live Streaming (HLS):"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " When playing HLS media, the player behaved as if "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": false,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1643482-automaticallywaitstominimizestal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " is "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": false,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "type": "strong",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "File-based Media:"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " When playing file-based media, including progressively downloaded content, the player behaved as if "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": false,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1643482-automaticallywaitstominimizestal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " is "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": false,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "You should verify that your playback applications perform as expected using this new default automatic waiting behavior."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "style": "important"
        }
      ]
    }
